  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TimeTrain is a simple but mind-bending puzzle game in which you create train routes through time as well as space. Tamper with temporality and cause chaos with causality across 50 brain-boggling puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number above each portal tells you how far back or forward in time it will send the train. To beat each level simply build a track that will send the TimeTrain to collect all the trophies scattered across the puzzle area. Be warned, however, as there are deadly traps that will destroy the TimeTrain if you do not deactivate them at the right time... and the right time might just be in the past or future!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TimeTrain is a simple but mind-bending puzzle game in which you create train routes through time as well as space. Tamper with temporality and cause chaos with causality across 50 brain-boggling puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number above each portal tells you how far back or forward in time it will send the train. To beat each level simply build a track that will send the TimeTrain to collect all the trophies scattered across the puzzle area. Be warned, however, as there are deadly traps that will destroy the TimeTrain if you do not deactivate them at the right time... and the right time might just be in the past or future!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
